title: Victoria Kemokai leaving IU women's basketball team for personal reasons
text:
Larger font size Posted: Monday, October 5, 2015 3:42 pm Victoria Kemokai leaving IU women's basketball team for personal reasons Jon Blau, The Hoosier Scoop heraldtimesonline.com | 0 comments 
Victoria Kemokai has left the Indiana women’s basketball team for personal reasons and will not return, according to a source.
